Coronavirus panic buyers stock up on Corona beer as brewing halted by Mexican government sparking global shortage fears</h1></section></header><div class="article__meta"><div class="article__name-date"><div class="article__author"><ul class="t-p-color article__noLabel article__ul" itemProp="author"><li class="article__author-list t-p-background-color__before"><span class="article__author-name t-p-color">Samantha Lock</span></li></ul></div><ul class="article__time"><li class="article__published"><span class="article__datestamp">3 Apr 2020, </span><span class="article__timestamp">11:10</span></li><li class="article__updated"><span class="article__datestamp"><span class="">Updated</span>: 3 Apr 2020, </span><span class="article__timestamp">14:54</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="article-switcheroo"><div class="article__content"><figure class="article__media"><div class="article__media-img-container open-gallery"><a href="#"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg" data-credit="" data-sizes="(max-width: 375px) 335px, (max-width: 520px) 480px, 620px" data-img="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960" data-srcSet="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=335 335w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=480 480w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=620 620w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=670 670w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=960 960w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1240 1240w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1005 1005w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1440 1440w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1860 1860w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1340 1340w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=1920 1920w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CORONAVIRUS-ADVICE-BANNER-v3.jpg?w=2480 2480w" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 4.2 1&quot;%3E%3C/svg%3E"/></a><div class="article__gallery-count"><span class="article__gallery-count-value">6</span></div></div></figure>
<p><strong>PANICKING beer lovers cleared shop shelves in Mexico of crates of Corona after production was halted due to the Covid-19 pandemic.</strong></p>
<p>The bottled lager - whose sales have been hammered since the outbreak - will be put on ice after the government in Mexico deemed it a non-essential product.</p>
<h3><b>⚠️ Read our</b> <b>coronavirus live blog</b><b> for the latest news &amp; updates</b></h3>
<figure class="article__media"><div class="article__media-img-container open-gallery" data-index="583070"><a href="#"><img alt=" People stock up with the beer after a government production ban was announced" class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg" data-credit="Newsflash/@valeriaturcios09" data-sizes="(max-width: 375px) 335px, (max-width: 520px) 480px, 620px" data-img="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=752" data-srcSet="https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=335 335w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=480 480w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=620 620w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=670 670w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=960 960w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1240 1240w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1005 1005w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1440 1440w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1860 1860w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1340 1340w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=1920 1920w, https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NINTCHDBPICT000574938411-e1585918151463.jpg?w=2480 2480w" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 0.8 1&quot;