yd-protesters-beat-cowardly-yob-attacked-woman/"><picture><source media="(max-width: 680px)" data-srcset="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/06/pmCOMPattack.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1" srcSet="" sizes="(min-width: 680px) 300px, 150px"/><source data-srcset="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/06/pmCOMPattack.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1" srcSet="" sizes="(min-width: 680px) 300px, 150px"/><img width="150" height="96" class="lazyload" alt="" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/06/pmCOMPattack.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1"/></picture></a><div class="teaser__item-play theme__background-color-rgba-80"><span></span></div></div></div><div class="rail__item-content"><span class="rail__item-sub"><h3 class="rail__item-headline t-p-color">SICK ATTACK</h3>Mob of George Floyd protesters beat up cowardly man who attacked innocent woman</span></div><div class="rail__item-cutoff"></div><a href="/news/5506384/george-floyd-protesters-beat-cowardly-yob-attacked-woman/" class="rail__item-anchor"></a></div><div class="rail__item swiper-slide"><div class="rail__item-image"><div class="teaser__image-container"><a href="/news/5516780/driver-george-floyd-protesters-seattle-gun/"><picture><source media="(max-width: 680px)" data-srcset="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/06/AD-COMPOSITE-Crazed-Gunman-2-2.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1" srcSet="" sizes="(min-width: 680px) 300px, 150px"/><source data-srcset="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/06/AD-COMPOSITE-Crazed-Gunman-2-2.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1" srcSet="" sizes="(min-width: 680px) 300px, 150px"/><img width="150" height="96" class="lazyload" alt="" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.thesun.ie/wp-content/uploads